    <h1 class="display-lg post-title">When To Refinance Mortgage: Complete Guide to Qualification, Rates & Process</h1>
    <div class="post-byline"><span class="mono">By Jim Blackburn · NMLS #1072866</span><span class="post-byline__sep">·</span><time datetime="2025-11-07">2025-11-07</time></div>
